title: John Klemmer - Finesse (1983) RESEED
description:
MP3/256Kbps

Finesse was released in 1983 and places the saxophonist in the company of bassist Bob Magnusson, keyboardist Russell Ferrante, drummer Ron McCurdy, and percussionist Steve Forman. This is jazz with real style and emotion in the light airy grooves. The music is sensual, sweet lyricism, or the sheer crystalline beauty of "Heart."
